      "QUOTE: Every atom in the universe carries the fingerprint of God. Nothing exists by accident; everything exists by design.",
      "PROPHETIC: I declare that as I study God's Word, He will open my eyes to see His hand in every area of my life — in creation, in circumstances, and in the details I have overlooked."
