      "God, remove every hindrance that prevents me from fully embracing this truth",
      "Lord, let Your Word concerning equality in Christ produce lasting fruit in my life",
      "Father, strengthen my faith as I meditate on Your promises in Galatians",
      "Lord Jesus, help me to be a living example of equality in Christ to those around me"
